oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.join

Class JoinGroupWritable

  • java.lang.Object
    • oracle.spatial.hadoop.vector.join.JoinGroupWritable

  • public class JoinGroupWritable
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the source data set and assigned partition information for a record . It is used as a key once a record from some data set is assigned to a partition.

    hsaucedo
